---
title: Beef Shepherd's Pie with Balsamic-Dressed Grape Salad
description: Heart-warming steak pie is a beloved English classic, but we've given this version a Canadian twist with flavourful beef to create a rich filling with veggies and thyme. Cut into that creamy, golden top and tuck in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-shepherd-s-pie-d57cf2a9.jpg
